summary: This article describes any leap year starting on Friday.
full_text:
This is the calendar for any leap year starting on Friday, January 1 , such as 1932, 1960, 1988, 2016, 2044 or 2072.
^ a b "Identical Calendar Years", hermetic.ch, 2011, webpage: Hermcal: lists 1904, 1932, 1960, 1988, 2016, 2044, 2072, 2112, 2140, 2168, 2196.
title: Leap year starting on Friday
